## Data Cleaning Process

The following steps were completed during data cleaning:

- Removed duplicate rows
- Removed null values
- Filtered negative ride durations
- Standardized column names and formats
- Converted datetime columns
- Created additional calculated fields:
  - ride_length
  - day_of_week
  - month
  - season

- Combined monthly datasets into a single cleaned dataset for analysis.
